-- Thai Siam Commercial Bank sees 2014 loan growth of 5 pct     
-- By Manunphattr Dhanananphorn
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 03:17AM EDT
-- None



BANGKOK, Aug 7 (Reuters) - Siam Commercial Bank <SCB.BK>, Thailand's third-largest lender by assets, said on Thursday it expected loan growth of 5 percent in 2014 from a year earlier after a pick-up in demand and improved economic outlook.

